{"tid":1932252,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"27歲男士由倫敦返港後 曾到沙田酒店出席20圍婚禮","createTime":"2020-03-18T15:16:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T16:05:57.000Z","uid":5195,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"57bf17519c92db163a2a24d430ce616304fa9d85","tid":1932252,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:16:02.000Z","msg":"【一名27歲男士由倫敦返港後 曾到沙田萬怡酒店出席婚禮】<br />\n衞生署衞生防護中心今日下午在記者會上公布，本港再多14宗武漢肺炎確診個案，另有8人初步呈陽性，創單日新高。其中第171宗個案是一名27歲男士，3月去過倫敦，返港後3月15日晚曾到沙田萬怡酒店出席婚禮，3月17日發燒，於威爾斯親王醫院留醫。中心指該場婚宴有20圍，賓客們圍枱而坐緊密接觸，因此當局正在追蹤部分賓客。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9437d3e0c8d4e50fa2341c0e01e22695bfa184ff","tid":1932252,"uid":20481,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:23:13.000Z","msg":"擺酒家族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2cd4d2eb22b83e9a1127a13b27a562ee3b2e4f","tid":1932252,"uid":33618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:24:43.000Z","msg":"痴撚線架喎啲人真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9518299bfb34d8eb48ca864b7b8a102bba437802","tid":1932252,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:26:38.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦<br />\n佢地唔介意變廢人, 行路都無氣, 邊阻到人"},{"pid":"e25c579ac67650f373faea86ac8c063fa9d4e573","tid":1932252,"uid":48973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:30:00.000Z","msg":"飲完又可以係隔離中心見"},{"pid":"56598f32de39ebda7e5328586641bbac5d0c8aa5","tid":1932252,"uid":111811,"li